cirrussearch-ignored-headings:
# 
# Övverschreffte, di beim Söhke överjange wähde.
# Änderonge werke vun däm Momang aan, woh di Sigg met dä Övverschreff neu önersöhk weed.
# Dat kann De sellver aanstivvelle, endäm dat De di Sigg afscheijschere deihß, derbei moß De nix draan verändert han.
# Syntax:
#   * Alles, wat en ener reih henger „#“ schteiht, bedüüg nix.
#   * Läddeje Reihje bedüüge nix.
#   * Reije met jät dren sin jenou de Övverschreffte, di nit opjenumme wääde, met jruuße un kleine Schreff.
Wäbsigge
Lohr och noh
 #
cirrussearch-boost-templates:
# 
# Sigge met eine vun heh dä Schablohne dren, wääde öm de aanjejovve Prozänte hühter aanjezeijsch.
# Änderonge werke vun däm Momang aan, woh heh di Sigg verändert wood.
# Syntax:
#   * Alles, wat en ener Reih henger „#“ schteiht, bedüüg nix.
#   * Läddeje Reihje bedüüge nix.
#   * Reije met jät dren sin jenou de Nahme vun dä Scheblohne - Appachtemangs sin müjjelesch, met jruuße un kleine Schreff. Dann küdd e |-Zeische un dernoh en Zahl un dernoh e %-Zeijsche.
# Beijschpelle, di et donn:
# Template:Johd|150%
# Template:Ärsch Ärsch Johd|300%
# Template:Schlääsch|50%
# Beijschpelle, di et nit donn:
# Template:Foo|150,234234% # Kein Kommas!
# Foo|150% <--- täschnesch jesinn deit et dat, ävver för et Enschlehße vun dä Sigg „Foo“ uss_em (nahmelohse) Houp-Appachtemang
# mer kann Änderone aan de Enschtällong pröhve, wam_mer en Frohch met:
#   boost-templates:"XX"
# derför schtällt, woh XX för di Nahm vun alle Schablohn schteiht, di mer ögersöhk han well, met Zweschreum derzwesche, un dat en eine Reih.
# Frohre di dat aanjävve övverjonn der ennhal vun däm Väld.
 #
cirrussearch-pref-desc: Probeer ons neu Projrammdeil zum Söhke. Et kann met mih Schprohche ömjonn, brängk flöker un neue Antwoote un kann esujaa Täx em Ennere vun Schablohne fenge.
cirrussearch-didyoumean-settings:
# 
# This message let you configure the settings of the "Did you mean" suggestions.
# Loor och op https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/search-suggesters-phrase.html
# Änderonge, di mer heh määt, werrke schtantepee.
# Syntax jehd esuh:
#   * Everything from a "#" character to the end of the line is a comment.
#   * Every non-blank line is the setting name followed by a ":" character followed by the setting value
# Settings are :
#   * max_errors (integer): the maximum number of the terms that at most considered to be misspellings in order to form a correction. 1 or 2.
#   * confidence (float): The confidence level defines a factor applied to the input phrases score which is used as a threshold for other suggest candidates. Only candidates that score higher than the threshold will be included in the result. For instance a confidence level of 1.0 will only return suggestions that score higher than the input phrase. If set to 0.0 the top N candidates are returned.
#   * min_doc_freq (float 0 to 1): The minimal threshold in number of documents a suggestion should appear in.
#                   High frequency terms are generally "stop words".
#   * max_term_freq (float 0 to 1): The maximum threshold in number of documents a suggest text token can exist in order to be included.
#   * prefix_length (integer): The number of minimal prefix characters that must match in order be a candidate suggestions.
#   * suggest_mode (missing, popular, always): The suggest mode controls what suggestions are included or controls for what suggest text terms, suggestions should be suggested.
# Examples of good lines:
# max_errors:2
# confidence:2.0
# max_term_freq:0.5
# min_doc_freq:0.01
# prefix_length:2
# suggest_mode:always
#
#
cirrussearch-query-too-long: Wat jesöhk wähde sull, es {{PLURAL:$1|eij|$1|kei}} Zeijsche lang. Dadd es länger, wi {{PLURAL:$1|eij|di $2|kei}} Zeijshe, di et Söhke zohlöht.
